{
  "snp3.4:0.1": "Sutta Nipāta 3.4 ",
  "snp3.4:0.2": "Pūraḷāsa (sundarikabhāradvāja) sutta ",
  "snp3.4:1.1": "Evaṁ me sutaṁ—",
  "snp3.4:1.2": " ekaṁ samayaṁ bhagavā kosalesu viharati sundarikāya nadiyā tīre. ",
  "snp3.4:1.3": "Tena kho pana samayena sundarikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo sundarikāya nadiyā tīre aggiṁ juhati, aggihuttaṁ paricarati. ",
  "snp3.4:1.4": "Atha kho sundarikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo aggiṁ juhitvā aggihuttaṁ paricaritvā uṭṭhāyāsanā samantā catuddisā anuvilokesi: ",
  "snp3.4:1.5": "“ko nu kho imaṁ habyasesaṁ bhuñjeyyā”ti? ",
  "snp3.4:1.6": "Addasā kho sundarikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṁ avidūre aññatarasmiṁ rukkhamūle sasīsaṁ pārutaṁ nisinnaṁ; ",
  "snp3.4:1.7": "disvāna vāmena hatthena habyasesaṁ gahetvā dakkhiṇena hatthena kamaṇḍaluṁ gahetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami. ",
  "snp3.4:2.1": "Atha kho bhagavā sundarikabhāradvājassa brāhmaṇassa padasaddena sīsaṁ vivari. ",
  "snp3.4:2.2": "Atha kho sundarikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo: “muṇḍo ayaṁ bhavaṁ, muṇḍako ayaṁ bhavan”ti tatova puna nivattitukāmo ahosi. ",
  "snp3.4:2.3": "Atha kho sundarikabhāradvājassa brāhmaṇassa etadahosi: ",
  "snp3.4:2.4": "“muṇḍāpi hi idhekacce brāhmaṇā bhavanti, yannūnāhaṁ upasaṅkamitvā jātiṁ puccheyyan”ti. ",
  "snp3.4:2.5": "Atha kho sundarikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṁ etadavoca: ",
  "snp3.4:2.6": "“kiṁjacco bhavan”ti? ",
  "snp3.4:3.1": "Atha kho bhagavā sundarikabhāradvājaṁ brāhmaṇaṁ gāthāhi ajjhabhāsi: ",
  "snp3.4:4.1": "“Na brāhmaṇo nomhi na rājaputto, ",
  "snp3.4:4.2": "Na vessāyano uda koci nomhi; ",
  "snp3.4:4.3": "Gottaṁ pariññāya puthujjanānaṁ, ",
  "snp3.4:4.4": "Akiñcano manta carāmi loke. ",
  "snp3.4:5.1": "Saṅghāṭivāsī agaho carāmi, ",
  "snp3.4:5.2": "Nivuttakeso abhinibbutatto; ",
  "snp3.4:5.3": "Alippamāno idha māṇavehi, ",
  "snp3.4:5.4": "Akallaṁ maṁ brāhmaṇa pucchasi gottapañhaṁ”. ",
  "snp3.4:6.1": "“Pucchanti ve bho brāhmaṇā brāhmaṇebhi, ",
  "snp3.4:6.2": "Saha brāhmaṇo no bhavan”ti. ",
  "snp3.4:7.1": "“Brāhmaṇo hi ce tvaṁ brūsi, ",
  "snp3.4:7.2": "Mañca brūsi abrāhmaṇaṁ; ",
  "snp3.4:7.3": "Taṁ taṁ sāvittiṁ pucchāmi, ",
  "snp3.4:7.4": "Tipadaṁ catuvīsatakkharaṁ”. ",
  "snp3.4:8.1": "“Kiṁ nissitā isayo manujā, ",
  "snp3.4:8.2": "Khattiyā brāhmaṇā devatānaṁ; ",
  "snp3.4:8.3": "Yaññamakappayiṁsu puthū idha loke”. ",
  "snp3.4:9.1": "“Yadantagū vedagū yaññakāle, ",
  "snp3.4:9.2": "Yassāhutiṁ labhe tassijjheti brūmi”. ",
  "snp3.4:10.1": "“Addhā hi tassa hutamijjhe, ",
  "snp3.4:10.2": "(iti brāhmaṇo) ",
  "snp3.4:10.3": "Yaṁ tādisaṁ vedagumaddasāma; ",
  "snp3.4:10.4": "Tumhādisānañhi adassanena, ",
  "snp3.4:10.5": "Añño jano bhuñjati pūraḷāsaṁ”. ",
  "snp3.4:11.1": "“Tasmātiha tvaṁ brāhmaṇa atthena, ",
  "snp3.4:11.2": "Atthiko upasaṅkamma puccha; ",
  "snp3.4:11.3": "Santaṁ vidhūmaṁ anīghaṁ nirāsaṁ, ",
  "snp3.4:11.4": "Appevidha abhivinde sumedhaṁ”. ",
  "snp3.4:12.1": "“Yaññe ratohaṁ bho gotama, ",
  "snp3.4:12.2": "Yaññaṁ yiṭṭhukāmo nāhaṁ pajānāmi; ",
  "snp3.4:12.3": "Anusāsatu maṁ bhavaṁ, ",
  "snp3.4:12.4": "Yattha hutaṁ ijjhate brūhi me taṁ”. ",
  "snp3.4:13.1": "“Tena hi tvaṁ, brāhmaṇa, odahassu sotaṁ; dhammaṁ te desessāmi—",
  "snp3.4:14.1": "Mā jātiṁ pucchī caraṇañca puccha, ",
  "snp3.4:14.2": "Kaṭṭhā have jāyati jātavedo; ",
  "snp3.4:14.3": "Nīcākulīnopi munī dhitīmā, ",
  "snp3.4:14.4": "Ājāniyo hoti hirīnisedho. ",
  "snp3.4:15.1": "Saccena danto damasā upeto, ",
  "snp3.4:15.2": "Vedantagū vūsitabrahmacariyo; ",
  "snp3.4:15.3": "Kālena tamhi habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.4:15.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.4:16.1": "Ye kāme hitvā agahā caranti, ",
  "snp3.4:16.2": "Susaññatattā tasaraṁva ujjuṁ; ",
  "snp3.4:16.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.4:16.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.4:17.1": "Ye vītarāgā susamāhitindriyā, ",
  "snp3.4:17.2": "Candova rāhuggahaṇā pamuttā; ",
  "snp3.4:17.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.4:17.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.4:18.1": "Asajjamānā vicaranti loke, ",
  "snp3.4:18.2": "Sadā satā hitvā mamāyitāni; ",
  "snp3.4:18.3": "Kālena tesu habyaṁ pavecche, ",
  "snp3.4:18.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo puññapekkho yajetha. ",
  "snp3.4:19.1": "Yo kāme hitvā abhibhuyyacārī, ",
  "snp3.4:19.2": "Yo vedi jātīmaraṇassa antaṁ; ",
  "snp3.4:19.3": "Parinibbuto udakarahadova sīto, ",
  "snp3.4:19.4": "Tathāgato arahati pūraḷāsaṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:20.1": "Samo samehi visamehi dūre, ",
  "snp3.4:20.2": "Tathāgato hoti anantapañño; ",
  "snp3.4:20.3": "Anūpalitto idha vā huraṁ vā, ",
  "snp3.4:20.4": "Tathāgato arahati pūraḷāsaṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:21.1": "Yamhi na māyā vasati na māno, ",
  "snp3.4:21.2": "Yo vītalobho amamo nirāso; ",
  "snp3.4:21.3": "Paṇunnakodho abhinibbutatto, ",
  "snp3.4:21.4": "Yo brāhmaṇo sokamalaṁ ahāsi; ",
  "snp3.4:21.5": "Tathāgato arahati pūraḷāsaṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:22.1": "Nivesanaṁ yo manaso ahāsi, ",
  "snp3.4:22.2": "Pariggahā yassa na santi keci; ",
  "snp3.4:22.3": "Anupādiyāno idha vā huraṁ vā, ",
  "snp3.4:22.4": "Tathāgato arahati pūraḷāsaṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:23.1": "Samāhito yo udatāri oghaṁ, ",
  "snp3.4:23.2": "Dhammaṁ caññāsi paramāya diṭṭhiyā; ",
  "snp3.4:23.3": "Khīṇāsavo antimadehadhārī, ",
  "snp3.4:23.4": "Tathāgato arahati pūraḷāsaṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:24.1": "Bhavāsavā yassa vacī kharā ca, ",
  "snp3.4:24.2": "Vidhūpitā atthagatā na santi; ",
  "snp3.4:24.3": "Sa vedagū sabbadhi vippamutto, ",
  "snp3.4:24.4": "Tathāgato arahati pūraḷāsaṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:25.1": "Saṅgātigo yassa na santi saṅgā, ",
  "snp3.4:25.2": "Yo mānasattesu amānasatto; ",
  "snp3.4:25.3": "Dukkhaṁ pariññāya sakhettavatthuṁ, ",
  "snp3.4:25.4": "Tathāgato arahati pūraḷāsaṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:26.1": "Āsaṁ anissāya vivekadassī, ",
  "snp3.4:26.2": "Paravediyaṁ diṭṭhimupātivatto; ",
  "snp3.4:26.3": "Ārammaṇā yassa na santi keci, ",
  "snp3.4:26.4": "Tathāgato arahati pūraḷāsaṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:27.1": "Paroparā yassa samecca dhammā, ",
  "snp3.4:27.2": "Vidhūpitā atthagatā na santi; ",
  "snp3.4:27.3": "Santo upādānakhaye vimutto, ",
  "snp3.4:27.4": "Tathāgato arahati pūraḷāsaṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:28.1": "Saṁyojanaṁ jātikhayantadassī, ",
  "snp3.4:28.2": "Yopānudi rāgapathaṁ asesaṁ; ",
  "snp3.4:28.3": "Suddho nidoso vimalo akāco, ",
  "snp3.4:28.4": "Tathāgato arahati pūraḷāsaṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:29.1": "Yo attano attānaṁ nānupassati, ",
  "snp3.4:29.2": "Samāhito ujjugato ṭhitatto; ",
  "snp3.4:29.3": "Sa ve anejo akhilo akaṅkho, ",
  "snp3.4:29.4": "Tathāgato arahati pūraḷāsaṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:30.1": "Mohantarā yassa na santi keci, ",
  "snp3.4:30.2": "Sabbesu dhammesu ca ñāṇadassī; ",
  "snp3.4:30.3": "Sarīrañca antimaṁ dhāreti, ",
  "snp3.4:30.4": "Patto ca sambodhimanuttaraṁ sivaṁ; ",
  "snp3.4:30.5": "Ettāvatā yakkhassa suddhi, ",
  "snp3.4:30.6": "Tathāgato arahati pūraḷāsaṁ”. ",
  "snp3.4:31.1": "“Hutañca mayhaṁ hutamatthu saccaṁ, ",
  "snp3.4:31.2": "Yaṁ tādisaṁ vedagunaṁ alatthaṁ; ",
  "snp3.4:31.3": "Brahmā hi sakkhi paṭigaṇhātu me bhagavā, ",
  "snp3.4:31.4": "Bhuñjatu me bhagavā pūraḷāsaṁ”. ",
  "snp3.4:32.1": "“Gāthābhigītaṁ me abhojaneyyaṁ, ",
  "snp3.4:32.2": "Sampassataṁ brāhmaṇa nesa dhammo; ",
  "snp3.4:32.3": "Gāthābhigītaṁ panudanti buddhā, ",
  "snp3.4:32.4": "Dhamme satī brāhmaṇa vuttiresā. ",
  "snp3.4:33.1": "Aññena ca kevalinaṁ mahesiṁ, ",
  "snp3.4:33.2": "Khīṇāsavaṁ kukkuccavūpasantaṁ; ",
  "snp3.4:33.3": "Annena pānena upaṭṭhahassu, ",
  "snp3.4:33.4": "Khettañhi taṁ puññapekkhassa hoti”. ",
  "snp3.4:34.1": "“Sādhāhaṁ bhagavā tathā vijaññaṁ, ",
  "snp3.4:34.2": "Yo dakkhiṇaṁ bhuñjeyya mādisassa; ",
  "snp3.4:34.3": "Yaṁ yaññakāle pariyesamāno, ",
  "snp3.4:34.4": "Pappuyya tava sāsanaṁ”. ",
  "snp3.4:35.1": "“Sārambhā yassa vigatā, ",
  "snp3.4:35.2": "Cittaṁ yassa anāvilaṁ; ",
  "snp3.4:35.3": "Vippamutto ca kāmehi, ",
  "snp3.4:35.4": "Thinaṁ yassa panūditaṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:36.1": "Sīmantānaṁ vinetāraṁ, ",
  "snp3.4:36.2": "Jātimaraṇakovidaṁ; ",
  "snp3.4:36.3": "Muniṁ moneyyasampannaṁ, ",
  "snp3.4:36.4": "Tādisaṁ yaññamāgataṁ. ",
  "snp3.4:37.1": "Bhakuṭiṁ vinayitvāna, ",
  "snp3.4:37.2": "Pañjalikā namassatha; ",
  "snp3.4:37.3": "Pūjetha annapānena, ",
  "snp3.4:37.4": "Evaṁ ijjhanti dakkhiṇā”. ",
  "snp3.4:38.1": "“Buddho bhavaṁ arahati pūraḷāsaṁ, ",
  "snp3.4:38.2": "Puññakhettamanuttaraṁ; ",
  "snp3.4:38.3": "Āyāgo sabbalokassa, ",
  "snp3.4:38.4": "Bhoto dinnaṁ mahapphalan”ti. ",
  "snp3.4:39.1": "Atha kho sundarikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṁ etadavoca: ",
  "snp3.4:39.2": "“abhikkantaṁ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṁ, bho gotama. ",
  "snp3.4:39.3": "Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṁ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṁ vā vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṁ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṁ dhāreyya: ‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti; evamevaṁ bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena dhammo pakāsito. ",
  "snp3.4:39.4": "Esāhaṁ bhavantaṁ gotamaṁ saraṇaṁ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca. ",
  "snp3.4:39.5": "Labheyyāhaṁ bhoto gotamassa santike pabbajjaṁ, labheyyaṁ upasampadan”ti. ",
  "snp3.4:39.6": "Alattha kho sundarikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo …pe… ",
  "snp3.4:39.7": "arahataṁ ahosīti. ",
  "snp3.4:39.8": "Sundarikabhāradvājasuttaṁ catutthaṁ. "
}